Class CefTraceClient

   |
   +--CefTraceClient
   in cef_trace.h
class CefTraceClient
extends CefBase

Implement this interface to receive trace notifications. The methods of this class will be called on the browser process UI thread.

Method Summary
 virtual void OnEndTracingComplete()
          Called after all processes have sent their trace data.

 virtual void OnTraceDataCollected( const char* fragment, size_t fragment_size )
